{"tid":986654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★拒參加自力更生計劃做義工，綜援婦揮刀稱「我唔想做人」！","createTime":"2019-01-18T15:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T06:51:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"69a0b0e9f01fc27d4e1d6bc337fde0130fa5a2b5","tid":986654,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20071025/large/25la3p13newa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20071025%2Flarge%2F25la3p13newa.jpg&h=62989fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天恩邨一名綜援婦人，被社署要求參與「自力更生支援計劃」，她拒絕參加並擔心被削減綜援金，返家後情緒失控，用生果刀架頸企圖自殺，警方到場將她勸服送院檢查。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">揮刀稱「我唔想做人」</span><br />\n<br />\n女事主姓郭（38歲），住天恩邨恩盈樓一單位，現場消息指，郭婦與女兒相依為命，她申領綜援多年，兩母女每月綜援金約6,000元，其女兒下月將15歲。社署發言人稱，根據家庭領綜援規定，家長需參加自力更生支援計劃做義工，否則綜援金會被削減。<br />\n據了解，社署職員昨與郭婦會面，職員解釋政策要她參與計劃，郭婦聲稱患有白內障，並以諸多理由推搪，職員表示若她不參加，她的綜援金會被削減，只剩下其女兒的一份，但如果有特殊理由亦可申請豁免。職員要她填寫表格，郭婦指職員有心留難，發脾氣拂袖而去。<br />\n至上午11時，郭婦返回家中，其時，有一名中年男性親友到訪，郭婦向他訴苦指受社署迫害，並越說越激動衝入廚房拿起一柄生果刀揮舞，並將生果刀架頸，聲稱：「我唔想做人，畀我死咗佢」，親友大驚立即制止並報警。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20071025/10335213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20071025%2F10335213&d=CGlvEuLvU3dvRpk9BeDIb%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=06eb2d7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20071025%2F10335213&h=3724d8b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20071025/10335213</a>"},{"pid":"337027139b7cee9df7b24f4be9141428d72946a9","tid":986654,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254d69db3cf582821ca7689c737cda7815c20808","tid":986654,"uid":20816,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:46:06.000Z","msg":"入硬青山醫院"},{"pid":"080a199626c384977335143c510889664456ed12","tid":986654,"uid":228143,"like":4,"dislike":32,"score":-28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:47:46.000Z","msg":"又話幾皮<br />\n得6千<br />\n又炒車"},{"pid":"ff8db1774afaffae4231cdb8a8c1bbb59e7da9c2","tid":986654,"uid":25424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:51:42.000Z","msg":"JoJo！"},{"pid":"785ab5a4f28e11dd2a863b79a28c2992d7f99e20","tid":986654,"uid":118120,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:56:38.000Z","msg":"大種乞兒<br />\n唔俾錢就要生要死, 全香港人欠左你一定要俾架."},{"pid":"b79db05d2d90dbd621615bde378c3c134d29ca9c","tid":986654,"uid":70789,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:56:42.000Z","msg":"係死先好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b83350dacc92f013d65d25995e282e3a1b90a4","tid":986654,"uid":46061,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"佢唔係唔想做人<br />\n係唔想做野啫"},{"pid":"35ed5880cd9be3d2e492a4a109f6cea491081dca","tid":986654,"uid":88029,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b96becd41f9f827cbc9b6c1867fc51646e1001d","tid":986654,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:09:13.000Z","msg":"Lazy china pig"},{"pid":"d01369c2b8b81dfc90c8ad2d9b99065b4dbf79c7","tid":986654,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:27:00.000Z","msg":"死啦仆街大陸婆"},{"pid":"3656e6888b187472ae2d58cc18e15bc247df2539","tid":986654,"uid":92376,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"2